- set_meta_tags default_meta_tags

%ul.post-list
  - articles.take(5).each do |article|
    %li.post-item
      %a.post-link{ href: article.path }
        %span.post-date= article.created_at.strftime("%Y.%m.%d")
        %span.post-title= article.title
        %span.post-excerpt= "#{CGI.escapeHTML(article.body_only_text[0..100])}..."

%a.more-link{ href: "/articles" } 記事一覧をすべて見る →
